.png", "id": "721350316815399", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982603_721350320148732_5117799024893724391_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LVPf-SC2nbMQ7kNvgFjEtnK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAP__dfBv4rp5dPT0CRm278mNK3YH2BGKifMDPbdwPa9g&oe=6783C41E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Primate.png", "id": "919902323212486", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974771_919902326545819_9171633814225842135_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DS3IPyd08LkQ7kNvgE8ISQM&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBVrZo9U4GSJK8C-oss8KITJ98SGnl-_qI-NaFs-AbIgw&oe=6783BEC2"}, "display_name": "Primate Mayhem", "keywords": [], "long_description": "After the showdown between the Kooky Monkes and the Phantom Monkey, everything was gone.... Everyone and Everything... The realm slowly pulsed back together and opened a realm... a realm full of Primates. In this new realm of primates, everyday brought new adventures as they embraced their freedom. And though the memory of the showdown between the Kooky Monkes and the Phantom Monkey lingered as a reminder of their past, it also served as a reminder to their determination to overcome any challenge that came their way.", "short_description": "After the showdown between the Kooky Monkes and the Phantom Monkey, everything was gone.... Everyone and Everything... The realm slowly pulsed back together and opened a realm... a realm full of Primates. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/capuplay/home", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "CapuPlay Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://kookymonkes.boxmode.io/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}]